Klasse Parser.Expression.Grouping

java.lang.Object
de.happybavarian07.coolstufflib.languagemanager.expressionengine.Parser.Expression
de.happybavarian07.coolstufflib.languagemanager.expressionengine.Parser.Expression.Grouping
Umschließende Klasse:
Parser.Expression
public static class Parser.Expression.Grouping extends Parser.Expression

Represents a grouped expression enclosed in parentheses that controls evaluation order. The grouping itself doesn't change the value but affects operator precedence.


 // Creates: (10 + 5) * 2
 Expression expr = new Binary(
     new Grouping(new Binary(new Literal(10), plusToken, new Literal(5))),
     multiplyToken,
     new Literal(2)
 );
